tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE AlgorithmData (
    data_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    input_data VARCHAR(255),
    output_data VARCHAR(255)
)

CREATE TABLE data_relations (
    relation_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    input_id INT,
    output_id INT,
    analysis_id INT,
    debugging_id INT,
    FOREIGN KEY (input_id) REFERENCES algorithm_input(input_id),
    FOREIGN KEY (output_id) REFERENCES algorithm_output(output_id),
    FOREIGN KEY (analysis_id) REFERENCES analysis_data(analysis_id),
    FOREIGN KEY (debugging_id) REFERENCES debugging_data(debugging_id)
);
